data.description: Extremely well maintained 3/2 home in Lady Lake that is located just a few minutes of all the dining and shopping in The Villages!! . This home is a two lot parcel, second lot is included in sale, over 1/4 acre. NO Hoa. Both lots are combined and are fenced. This home features tile floors throughout the entire home, a split open floor plan, and a screened back porch. Public water is currently connected. This is a magnificently valued home in the neighborhood and will not last long! Schedule your showing ASAP!!!
